I was struggle with your same problem, so I found this helpful [post](https://dzone.com/articles/spring-boot-metrics-with-dynamic-tag-values), but...
I didn&#39;t liked this solution.

I think te better approach is a placeholder one, like [this](https://github.com/micrometer-metrics/micrometer/issues/620).
So maybe define a `HierarchicalNameMapper` that will replace tag placeholder when tag keys match it, it&#39;s good choice.

